  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your unarmed strikes weave together in an effortless combo, focusing on the spots you've weakened with the last hit.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Improved Unarmed Strike; base attack bonus +6, brawler's flurry class feature, or flurry of blows class feature.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever you use a full-attack action or flurry of blows to make multiple attacks against a single opponent with unarmed strikes, total the damage from all hits before applying damage reduction. This ability works only with unarmed strikes, no matter what other abilities you might possess.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>While using this style, you can spend 5 stamina points to pool all of your attacks as a standard action, instead of a full-round action.",
